metadata.name: CEQ #1
metadata.description: Utterances of a former crypto trading giantess.

attributes.value: What I am reeally into is contrarianism and being an edgelord, and what's been most successful in getting me into feelings talk is framing it through that lens: basically "I'm so cool and edgy, I'm willing to talk about my feelings and be vulnerable even if it's socially weird or whatever."
